          "insert": " reducer over the single "
        },
        {
          "insert": "CanvasAction",
          "attributes": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " union — there is no second write path. This guarantees consistent undo/history behavior and consistent connector-waypoint reconciliation no matter which caller mutated the document, since every mutation is a typed action passing through the same authority rather than an ad hoc state patch."
        }
      ],
